title: project skins
body: I'm not able to buy any of the new project skins. anytime I go to look at them it says unavailable. is there a reason for this that I'm un aware off?

replies.body: The new skins mentioned in the[ patch notes](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/game-updates/patch/patch-615-notes#patch-upcoming-skins) have not yet been released.  Keep an eye on our [news page](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/) for announcements on any new content!  Hang in there!
Releasing new products on payday is smarter than releasing them midweek.

They simply are not released yet. They are scheduled to release sometime this patch unless some issues crop up, but it could be any time between right now and right before the servers shut down for the next patch. I would expect them next Wednesday at the latest.
Wtf are u, a Rito errand boy?
